description: Set dashboard provides specific set level metrics as well as helping in tracking and setting specific set quotas.

targets.expr: count by (severity) (ALERTS{job="$job_name", cluster_name=~"$cluster", service=~"$node", ns=~"$namespace|$^", severity=~"warn|critical|info|error", set=~"$set",})
count_values("dis_evict", (aerospike_sets_disable_eviction{job="$job_name", cluster_name=~"$cluster|$^",  service=~"$node|$^", ns=~"$namespace", set=~"$set",} or on() vector(-1)))
count_values("enable_idx",aerospike_sets_enable_index{job="$job_name", cluster_name=~"$cluster|$^",  service=~"$node|$^", ns=~"$namespace", set=~"$set",} or on() vector(-1))
count_values("stop_write_size", aerospike_sets_stop_writes_size{job="$job_name", cluster_name=~"$cluster|$^",  service=~"$node|$^", ns=~"$namespace", set=~"$set",} or on() vector(-1))

panels.description: Set Quota usage against "stop write size" configuration

targets.expr:
topk( $set_quota_topk,sort_desc((
  (aerospike_sets_memory_data_bytes{job="$job_name",cluster_name=~"$cluster", service=~"$node|$^", ns=~"$namespace|$^", set=~"$set",}+aerospike_sets_device_data_bytes{job="$job_name",cluster_name=~"$cluster", service=~"$node|$^", ns=~"$namespace|$^", set=~"$set",})
  /(aerospike_sets_stop_writes_size{job="$job_name",cluster_name=~"$cluster", service=~"$node|$^", ns=~"$namespace|$^", set=~"$set",}!=0) )*100))

topk( $set_quota_topk, sort_desc((
  (aerospike_sets_data_used_bytes{job="$job_name",cluster_name=~"$cluster", service=~"$node|$^", ns=~"$namespace|$^", set=~"$set",})
  /(aerospike_sets_stop_writes_size{job="$job_name",cluster_name=~"$cluster", service=~"$node|$^", ns=~"$namespace|$^", set=~"$set",}!=0) )*100) )

panels.title: % Set Quota Used (topk)
